more monoecious trees.

00:13:58.540 --> 00:14:00.840
There are no female flowers.

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:03.860
They've been grafted
with parts from the male.

00:14:03.860 --> 00:14:06.550
That means they won't
drop any messy pods.

00:14:06.550 --> 00:14:10.440
But it means that the parking
lot is already allergenic.

00:14:10.440 --> 00:14:14.320
And 5 years from now, it's
going to be 20 times more.

00:14:14.320 --> 00:14:17.150
Three of the ones that I'm the
most interested, dioecious,

00:14:17.150 --> 00:14:18.640
separate sex.

00:14:18.640 --> 00:14:20.150
Everybody here is dioecious.

00:14:20.150 --> 00:14:24.650
