00:14:34.960 --> 00:14:39.620
But around 30 years ago I was
sitting in bed with my wife.

00:14:39.620 --> 00:14:43.450
And I was reading a book
on pollen, big thick thing

00:14:43.450 --> 00:14:45.330
that almost nobody reads.

00:14:45.330 --> 00:14:47.430
And she was reading a novel.

00:14:47.430 --> 00:14:49.690
And I kept reading
about those separate sex

00:14:49.690 --> 00:14:53.430
dioecious species that's
causing so much allergies.

00:14:53.430 --> 00:14:55.990
And some were even saying,
don't plant any of these.

00:14:55.990 --> 00:14:58.490
And they include
hundreds of plants.

00:14:58.490 --> 00:15:02.170
And I suddenly got
this bright idea.

00:15:02.170 --> 00:15:04.700
And I said to my wife,
I said, Yvonne, I said,

00:15:04.700 --> 00:15:05.750
I've got this idea.

00:15:05.750 --> 00:15:06.833
And she said, what's that?

