00:27:04.860 --> 00:27:08.280
OK so real quickly, all
trees are not equal.

00:27:08.280 --> 00:27:10.520
And I get very
irritated when the city

00:27:10.520 --> 00:27:13.060
says we're going to plant
a million new trees.

00:27:13.060 --> 00:27:15.736
My question, yeah, OK,
what kind of trees?

00:27:15.736 --> 00:27:17.480
Uh, trees.

00:27:17.480 --> 00:27:19.100
But trees are like people.

00:27:19.100 --> 00:27:20.680
Some of us are hard working.

00:27:20.680 --> 00:27:21.880
Some are lazy.

00:27:21.880 --> 00:27:22.750
Some are dumb.

00:27:22.750 --> 00:27:24.140
Some are smart.

00:27:24.140 --> 00:27:25.140
Some are friendly.

00:27:25.140 --> 00:27:27.030
Some are not friendly.

00:27:27.030 --> 00:27:28.050
Trees are the same way.

