removed all these males trees

00:29:27.310 --> 00:29:30.300
out of the place
and replaced them

00:29:30.300 --> 00:29:33.080
with the clonal
female red maple.

00:29:33.080 --> 00:29:34.960
And they're now big and
beautiful shade trees

00:29:34.960 --> 00:29:37.200
and they're not
producing any allergies.

00:29:37.200 --> 00:29:39.730
I see a lot more of
that down the road.

00:29:39.730 --> 00:29:44.940
But there was a Minnesota
Law Review article on it,

00:29:44.940 --> 00:29:47.550
and so the stage is
sort of set for that.

00:29:47.550 --> 00:29:50.890
But it'd be better if we could
do it without litigation.

00:29:50.890 --> 00:29:51.696
