00:31:50.800 --> 00:31:53.260
And so we came up with that.

00:31:53.260 --> 00:31:54.460
It got me on NPR.

00:31:54.460 --> 00:31:56.610
We had some fun with it.

00:31:56.610 --> 00:31:59.750
That's a carob tree, and
