00:32:10.400 --> 00:32:16.000
This is a female bay
tree, very, very rare item

00:32:16.000 --> 00:32:17.800
and very hard to find.

00:32:17.800 --> 00:32:20.090
The only person I know
besides me that has one

00:32:20.090 --> 00:32:24.280
