00:33:22.350 --> 00:33:25.740
It's planted outside
an old church in Poland

00:33:25.740 --> 00:33:27.360
and it's a yew.

00:33:27.360 --> 00:33:30.470
Yews are 100% male or female.

00:33:30.470 --> 00:33:33.040
And this particular
tree is a female.

00:33:33.040 --> 00:33:35.870
Now whoever planted that
yew, if it had been a male,

00:33:35.870 --> 00:33:37.551
that pollen would
go into the church

00:33:37.551 --> 00:33:39.050
when they were there
and everything.

00:33:39.050 --> 00:33:41.670
But no, this tree
