00:34:26.659 --> 00:34:29.440
But what's interesting
about that plant-- which

00:34:29.440 --> 00:34:32.199
is a relative to
this, it just takes

00:34:32.199 --> 00:34:36.650
more cold weather-- is that
that plant is poisonous

00:34:36.650 --> 00:34:41.130
and this plant is poisonous, but
the fruits are not poisonous.

00:34:41.130 --> 00:34:43.260
But the seeds are poisonous.

00:34:43.260 --> 00:34:45.320
But the pollen is poisonous.

00:34:45.320 --> 00:34:50.600
Now from that plant, they make
Taxol, a chemotherapy drug

00:34:50.600 --> 00:34:51.620
for breast cancer.

00:34:51.620 --> 00:34:56.210
From this, they make
[? Podocarpaceae ?] it's called

00:34:56.210 --> 00:35:01.060
or something, and it's a
chemotherapy drug for leukemia.

00:35:01.060 --> 00:35:06.590
Now chemo drugs have all these.

00:35:06.590 --> 00:35:10.800
The idea is to kill the cancer
before we kill the patient.

00:35:10.800 --> 00:35:14.670
So I've encountered many people
over the years who are sick.

00:35:14.670 --> 00:35:16.400
Nobody knows what's wrong.

00:35:16.400 --> 00:35:20.540
None of the testings
show what the cause is.

